I'm now integrating the rotation smoothing, incorporating angle wrapping to ensure smooth transitions in the `updatePhysics` method. I'm adding a distance check to conditionally skip collision, and applying `moveVec` and `velocity` appropriately. This is going to be tested for smoothness in comparison to the old method. I am also planning on modifying the `index.html` file to test this modification.


